xmppipe is an XMPP component (XEP-0114) that can receive messages and
pipe the result as a JSON format to any other binary over STDIN and send
from external utilities over a Unix stream socket.

Notable Perl library dependencies:
- JSON
- Net::Jabber / Net::XMPP
- Config::General
- Sys::Syslog

Author: Pascal Lalonde <plalonde@overnet.ca>
